<paragraph id="IFRS03_46" base="F4230542" principles="no"><paranum>46</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 3"/><data name="paranum" value="46"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS03_P0180">The measurement period is the period after the <xref base="F4230836" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0298">acquisition date<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0006"/></ph></xref> during which the <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref> may adjust the provisional amounts recognised for a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref>. The measurement period provides the acquirer with a reasonable time to obtain the information necessary to identify and measure the following as of the acquisition date in accordance with the requirements of this IFRS:</p><ol id="IFRS03_L0020" base="F4230544" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0181" base="F4230545">the <xref base="F4230861" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0314">identifiable<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0174"/></ph></xref> assets acquired, liabilities assumed and any <xref base="F4230876" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0323">non&#x2011;controlling interest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0260"/></ph></xref> in the <xref base="F4230829" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0296">acquiree<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0004"/></ph></xref>;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0182" base="F4230547">the consideration transferred for the acquiree (or the other amount used in measuring <xref base="F4230858" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0311">goodwill<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0147"/></ph></xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0183" base="F4230549">in a business combination achieved in stages, the <xref base="F4230851" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0308">equity interest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0104"/></ph></xref> in the acquiree previously held by the acquirer; and</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0184" base="F4230551">the resulting goodwill or gain on a bargain purchase.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>